model = DistMult(batches_count=2, seed=555, epochs=20, k=10, loss=
    'pairwise', loss_params={'margin': 5}, optimizer='adagrad',
    optimizer_params={'lr': 0.1})
X = np.array([['a', 'y', 'b'], ['b', 'y', 'a'], ['a', 'y', 'c'], ['c', 'y',
    'a'], ['a', 'y', 'd'], ['c', 'y', 'd'], ['b', 'y', 'c'], ['f', 'y', 'e']])
model.fit(X)
y_pred = model.predict(np.array([['f', 'y', 'e'], ['b', 'y', 'd']]))
print(y_pred)
assert y_pred[0] > y_pred[1]
